title: MakerBot Screwdriver
description: Experience the convenience of this compact MakerBot Screwdriver. Crafted as a singular piece, it's perfect for all your light-duty tasks. Its small size makes it an indispensable tool in tight spaces.

title: MakerBot Plate
description: Discover the enigmatic MakerBot Plate. This intriguing piece boasts an oblong design, about four inches in length, with a subtle flare at each end. Its surface is adorned with an intriguing pattern of ridges, and it features several uniquely placed square holes. Its purpose is a mystery that's waiting to be uncovered!

title: MakerBot Hook
description: Introducing the MakerBot Hook - a double-ended hook that is reminiscent of a shower curtain hook. Perfect for multipurpose use and designed to bring convenience and organization to your space!

title: 1st stellation of a dodecahedron
description: Experience the beauty of geometry with this intricately designed model of the first stellation of a dodecahedron. Perfect for hands-on learning or as a decorative piece, this model is crafted to fit '172' illustration boards. Feel free to resize the parts if you wish to use different materials for construction. Explore and appreciate the wonders of mathematical shapes with this model.

title: MakerBot Knob
description: Introducing the MakerBot Knob - a compact, stylish knob with a unique blocky design. It features three flanges for an enhanced grip, making it perfect for high-use situations. The knob is also designed with a distinctive pentagonal hole in the center, adding to its appeal.
